{"tid":1945329,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"葉劉:人權自由非絕對 倡限人群聚集","createTime":"2020-03-27T03:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-27T04:47:13.000Z","uid":187957,"like":1,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"cb457c4d648cf9053d38a37cd18897b85d6d3987","tid":1945329,"uid":187957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:36:13.000Z","msg":"行政會議下午會召開特別會議，討論進一步抗疫措施，預料討論是否落實推行「禁酒令」、限制公眾社交活動，限定外出聚集人數，以防止人群聚集及截斷傳播鏈。<br />\n<br />\n行會成員葉劉淑儀認為，本港已經處於公共衛生緊急狀態，政府有權引用《預防及控制疾病條例》對人群聚集的活動施加限制，相信政府修例時不會針對每一種情況，而是從一些原則要求作出規範。<br />\n<br />\n葉劉淑儀指出，政府毋須仿傚外國推行「禁足令」，但有需要限制人群聚集，包括外傭假日外出聚會，減低病毒傳播風險，強調人權和自由並非絕對，在公共衞生、國家安全等前提下，可以作出合理限制。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2416565/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%3A%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%9D%9E%E7%B5%95%E5%B0%8D+%E5%80%A1%E9%99%90%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2416565%2F%25E8%2591%2589%25E5%258A%2589%253A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25B5%2595%25E5%25B0%258D%2B%25E5%2580%25A1%25E9%2599%2590%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E8%2581%259A%25E9%259B%2586&d=UCgs38VSsqZrRa6JqpzgNjbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=98c8640f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2416565/%E8%91%89%E5%8A%89%3A%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%E9%9D%9E%E7%B5%95%E5%B0%8D+%E5%80%A1%E9%99%90%E4%BA%BA%E7%BE%A4%E8%81%9A%E9%9B%86</a>"},{"pid":"f00a8473c617338bc86ccef5ac5646eca5f5163d","tid":1945329,"uid":2192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:36:54.000Z","msg":"兩樣野攞埋來講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1831f9e4f09e43279a1c722f8b4600593809285","tid":1945329,"uid":187957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-27T03:37:31.000Z","msg":"在<span style=\"color: red;\">公共衞生</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"f